      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;CM-400 Dongfeng 61&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 4 waypoint-capable cruise missile.  It is based on the CM-4 body, which is a heavy anti-ship torpedo.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_HEIMPACT warhead.  It homes in on its target using an Active Radar seeker, validating that it is the correct target using a Passive Wake seeker.

